			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="This dialogue occurs if the player has sided with the hag in the ambush and saved her - by killing the brothers.&#xA;She's still in old lady mode, hamming up how upset she is, but there should be a hint on the last set of questions, about the gold, that this was an act and that there is more to her than meets the eye. " />
